# Project Rules
These rules define the required standards for structure, naming, styling, accessibility, and conventions across this project.
Cursor must follow these rules strictly when generating or modifying code.

---

# 1. Project Structure
## 1.1 Component Directories
- The project contains two primary shared component directories:
  - `component/canggu/*` — **Do not modify. Do not install dependencies. Do not introduce major changes.**  
    This directory contains custom components derived from `shadcn/ui`.
  - `component/utility/*` — Shared utilities.

## 1.2 Application-Level Components
- Components for app-level and route-level usage must live inside the relevant `app/**/component` directory.
- Examples:
  - `app/component/layout/navigation.tsx`
  - `app/component/page/hero.tsx`
  - `app/component/page/achievement.tsx`
  - `app/about/component/page/hero.tsx`

